#: src/Errors/AmazonApiError.php:64
msgid ""
"Looks like there's a configuration issue with your Amazon Associates account."
" The access key you provided is not linked to a primary store in your "
"approved Amazon Associates account. To fix this, head over to Associate "
"Central and check your account settings. Make sure the access key you're "
"using is associated with a primary store that's been approved by Amazon "
"Associates."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay un problema de configuración con tu cuenta de Amazon "
"Associates. La clave de acceso que compartiste no está vinculada a una "
"tienda principal en tu cuenta de Amazon Associates aprobada. Para "
"solucionarlo, dirígete a Associate Central y comprueba la configuración de "
"tu cuenta. Asegúrate de que la clave de acceso que usas está asociada a una "
"tienda principal aprobada por Amazon Associates."

#: src/Errors/AmazonApiError.php:94
msgid ""
"Looks like there's a configuration issue with your Amazon Associates account."
" The access key you provided is not valid. To fix this, head over to "
"Associate Central and check your account settings."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay un problema de configuración con tu cuenta de Amazon "
"Associates. La clave de acceso que compartiste no es válida. Para "
"solucionarlo, dirígete a Associate Central y comprueba la configuración de "
"tu cuenta."

#: src/Errors/AmazonApiError.php:69
msgid ""
"Looks like there's a configuration issue with your Amazon Associates account."
" The partner tag you provided is not linked to the access key you’re using. "
"To fix this, head over to Associate Central and check your account settings. "
"Make sure the partner tag you're using is associated with a valid store in "
"your Amazon Associates account for the requested marketplace."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay un problema de configuración con tu cuenta de Amazon "
"Associates. La etiqueta de socio que compartiste no está vinculada a la "
"clave de acceso que estás utilizando. Para solucionarlo, dirígete a "
"Associate Central y comprueba la configuración de tu cuenta. Asegúrate de "
"que la etiqueta de socio que estás usando está asociada a una tienda válida "
"en tu cuenta de Amazon Associates para el mercado solicitado."

#: src/Errors/AmazonApiError.php:96
msgid ""
"Make sure the access key you're using is correct. If you're still having "
"trouble after checking your settings, contact Amazon Associates support for "
"further assistance."
msgstr ""
"Asegúrate de que la clave de acceso que estás usando es correcta. Si sigues "
"teniendo problemas después de comprobar la configuración, contacta con el "
"servicio de asistencia de Amazon Associates para obtener más ayuda."

